   Welcome to the Researchers and Health Professionals section of our
   site. This section offers valuable information for researchers and
   health professionals including information about our international
   program, our training programs, and various NIDA committees and work
   groups. Materials in this section are public domain and may be
   reproduced, unless otherwise noted.
